salted caramel hot chocolate.author: cadence p.
salted caramel hot chocolate.review: Love coming to this spot since it's open 24/7. Having that said, it helps me fulfill my random cravings at 2am. My favorite drinks to get so far are.. White Chocolate Mocha HOT/COLD. Sometimes with a pump of Hazelnut. Passion Fruit Lemonade. Pumpkin Spice Latte. Salted Caramel Hot Chocolate. Caramel Brulee Latte. Hot/Cold. Occasionally would buy some Madelines as well hehe :)
